http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Hyderabad/SBH-gets-two-GMs/article14616184.ece

State Bank of Hyderabad (SBH) announced that Rajiv Sharma and Sudhir Thakore assumed charge as General Managers on Tuesday. Mr. Sharma, who assumed charge as GM-Hyderabad Network, joined SBH in 1982 as a Probationary Officer and held several assignments in the bank.Mr. Thakore assumed charge as GM-Inspection and Audit, Credit Policy and Procedure and Official Language Department at the SBH head office. He joined State Bank of Bikaner and Jaipur in 1985 as a Rural Development Officer. He was also DGM at State Bank of Travancore.